widgets_values: A photograph of an Asian woman standing outdoors, smiling warmly at the camera. She has fair skin, long black hair styled in a side braid, and wears gold hoop earrings. She is dressed in a green V-neck short-sleeve top and a high-waisted red skirt with a pleated design. Her red lipstick matches her skirt, and she has a slender build. The sunlight filters through the greenery behind her, creating a soft, warm glow. The image has a shallow depth of field, making the background blurry and focusing on her.
